"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.12\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.12</span> 標題：倉庫、庫房（storehouse）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת, אָסֹף</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： (beyth) ’asupim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:25\">NEH 12:25</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אוֹצָר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’otsar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:27\">1CH 27:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:28\">1CH 27:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr11:11\">2CH 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:44\">NEH 12:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:12\">NEH 13:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:13\">NEH 13:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:22\">JOB 38:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:22\">JOB 38:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:7\">PSA 33:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:7\">PSA 135:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:2\">ISA 39:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:4\">ISA 39:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:13\">JER 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:11\">JER 38:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:16\">JER 51:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἀποδοχεῖον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： apodocheion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir1:17\">SIR 1:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： θησαυρός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： thēsauros)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir41:12\">SIR 41:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir43:14\">SIR 43:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ταμεῖον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tameion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:24\">LUK 12:24</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>上面列出的經文都是指一般用途的庫房，並未明確說明其形狀和結構。另參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.4 軍械庫、武器庫 (armory, arsenal)&lt;REALIA:3.13.4&gt;</a> 和<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.14.1.4 庫房、銀庫、寶庫 (treasury, strongroom)&lt;REALIA:3.14.1.4&gt;</a> 。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>上面列出的大部分經文都說明了其中儲存的是什麼。如果經文說明了儲存貨物的名稱，目標語言可能會有專門的名稱來稱呼這些地方；例如，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:27\">1CH 27:27</a> 中，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 把希伯來文<em>’otsar</em> 譯為“Wine cellars”（「酒窖」）。然而，在接下來的一節經文中，同一個詞語與「油」一起使用時，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 譯為“Olive oil storage”（「橄欖油倉庫」），因為英文沒有專門的詞語來表示儲存橄欖油的地方。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
