"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.12.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.12.1</span> 標題：糧倉、倉房、倉廩（grain-store, silo）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אָסָם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’asam)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:8\">DEU 28:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:10\">PRO 3:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אוֹצָר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’otsar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:17\">JOL 1:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַאֲבוּס</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ma’avus)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:26\">JER 50:26</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מְגוּרָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mgurah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:19\">HAG 2:19</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַמְּגוּרָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mamgurah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:17\">JOL 1:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מִסְכְּנוֹת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： misknoth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:11\">EXO 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:19\">1KI 9:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:4\">2CH 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:6\">2CH 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:4\">2CH 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:12\">2CH 17:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:28\">2CH 32:28</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： ἀποθήκη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： apothēkē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:12\">MAT 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:26\">MAT 6:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:30\">MAT 13:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:17\">LUK 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:18\">LUK 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:24\">LUK 12:24</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Latin</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">拉： promptuarium</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd5:9\">2ES 5:9</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0419_grain_store.jpg\" alt=\"米吉多的穀倉\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">米吉多的穀倉 (© Ian Scott, CC BY-SA 2.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>糧倉是用來儲存農產品的一種小型構築物，通常用石頭砌成。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在許多語言中，用來儲存農產品的建築物和用來儲存其他東西的倉庫具有重要的區別。這裡所討論的構築物實際上並不是一座「建築」，因為它並不是像房子那樣建成的。英文單詞“barn”（「倉房」）表達的是一個很大、多用途的構築物。翻譯者可以優先考慮「糧倉」、「穀倉」或「糧庫」等詞語。</p>\n<p>在大部分參考經文中（除了<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:28\">2CH 32:28</a> ），希伯來文<em>misknoth</em> 都與「城」一詞同時出現。以下是《〈出埃及記〉手冊》（<em>A Handbook on Exodus</em> ，第22頁）對<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:11\">EXO 1:11</a> 所提出的意見：「『儲貨城』是特別為政府建造的儲物中心，用作儲存糧食和其他物資的倉庫。如果目標語言的文化不知道這類中心，可以遵循<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Today&#x27;s English Version (Good News Bible)\">TEV</abbr> （即<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）的譯法，把該詞譯為『儲存物資的城市』或『作供應中心的城市』。在有些文化中，唯一的大型人類聚居地就是由柵欄包圍的村莊，在這種情況下，翻譯者要採用比較詳細的描述來翻譯『儲貨城』；例如，『用來儲存各種物質、四周有高牆（或：柵欄）的大村莊』，或『用來儲存糧食和其他東西，四周用柵欄圍起來的、很大的地方』。」</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
